				<td colspan="2"><span><blockquote><b>Quote:</b><br><span class="quote">My guild will hate me for sharing secret, but, i hope you guys would do the same, if i need help so here it is, What u do is have a rogue sneak through tunnels with SoS ( shroud of stealth AA ) and then what u do is have everyone stand near ledge and duel each other til the death then drag corpse onto the hill. Then rez for 96%, not much lost exp and way easier to get everyone up and the ast person left can duel a caster on the ledge, and can just get nuked to death.</span></blockquote>
<br />

<br />

<br />
Way back when I was running small raids to kill Vhaksiz we used this tactic when it was posted on tCH. I had people duel but found it too slow. Now I tell everyone to move right up against the wall and sit. Then I go pull a train and dump it on my guildies. In a few seconds they'll all be dead and they can consent you to CR them back up while the cleric runs back to the plateau edge.
<br />

